<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>For Ashmita ❤️</title>

<style>
body{
margin:0;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9a9e,#fad0c4);
font-family:'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
overflow:hidden;
}

.envelope{
background:white;
padding:20px 40px;
border-radius:12px;
font-size:22px;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
transition:0.3s;
}

.envelope:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

.letter{
display:none;
background:white;
padding:40px;
border-radius:20px;
width:360px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
animation:fadeIn 1.5s;
}

h1{
color:#ff4d6d;
}

p{
color:#444;
font-size:16px;
}

button{
margin-top:15px;
padding:10px 20px;
border:none;
background:#ff4d6d;
color:white;
border-radius:10px;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
bottom:-20px;
font-size:20px;
animation:float 6s linear infinite;
}

.confetti{
position:absolute;
top:-10px;
font-size:18px;
animation:fall 5s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{transform:translateY(0);}
100%{transform:translateY(-100vh);}
}

@keyframes fall{
0%{transform:translateY(0);}
100%{transform:translateY(110vh);}
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px);}
to{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="envelope" onclick="openLetter()">
💌 Tap to Open
</div>

<div class="letter" id="letter">

<h1 id="title"></h1>

<p>Hey Ashmita,</p>

<p>I made this little birthday surprise just for you.</p>

<p>I know I made some mistakes and I’m really sorry.</p>

<p>I just wanted you to know that I miss you a lot.</p>

<p>No matter what happens, you will always be special to me.</p>

<p>Happy Birthday 🎂</p>

<p>— Sunny ❤️</p>

<button onclick="forgive()">क्या तुम मुझे माफ़ करोगी?</button>

<p id="reply"></p>

</div>

<audio id="music" loop>
<source src="https://www.bensound.com/bensound-music/bensound-love